{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendskpaymenttransactions:"]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendSKPaymentTransactions:"}],"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)sendSKPaymentTransactions:","role":"symbol","title":"sendSKPaymentTransactions:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"sendSKPaymentTransactions:","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sends StoreKit payment transactions to Pushwoosh for purchase tracking."}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendSKPaymentTransactions:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"transactions","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"transactions","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Array of "},{"code":"SKPaymentTransaction","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" objects from StoreKit.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Automatically tracks in-app purchases from StoreKit transactions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"This enables:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Revenue tracking"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Monitor purchase revenue in Pushwoosh dashboard"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Purchase-based segmentation"}]},{"text":": Target paying users, high-value customers","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"LTV analysis","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Calculate customer lifetime value","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Purchase events","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Trigger automations based on purchases"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method from your "},{"code":"SKPaymentTransactionObserver","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" for all","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"completed transactions."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Integrate with StoreKit payment observer:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class StoreKitManager: NSObject, SKPaymentTransactionObserver {","","    func paymentQueue(_ queue: SKPaymentQueue,","                     updatedTransactions transactions: [SKPaymentTransaction]) {","","        let completedTransactions = transactions.filter {","            $0.transactionState == .purchased || $0.transactionState == .restored","        }","","        \/\/ Send completed transactions to Pushwoosh","        if !completedTransactions.isEmpty {","            Pushwoosh.configure.sendSKPaymentTransactions(completedTransactions)","        }","","        \/\/ Process each transaction","        for transaction in transactions {","            switch transaction.transactionState {","            case .purchased:","                handlePurchase(transaction)","                queue.finishTransaction(transaction)","","            case .restored:","                handleRestore(transaction)","                queue.finishTransaction(transaction)","","            case .failed:","                handleFailure(transaction)","                queue.finishTransaction(transaction)","","            case .deferred, .purchasing:","                break","","            @unknown default:","                break","            }","        }","    }","","    private func handlePurchase(_ transaction: SKPaymentTransaction) {","        let productId = transaction.payment.productIdentifier","","        \/\/ Update user tags for purchase segmentation","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"has_purchased\": true,","            \"last_purchase_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","            \"last_purchased_product\": productId","        ])","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendSKPaymentTransactions:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/sendSKPaymentTransactions:":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sendSKPaymentTransactions:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"sendSKPaymentTransactions:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendskpaymenttransactions:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendSKPaymentTransactions:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sends StoreKit payment transactions to Pushwoosh for purchase tracking."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendSKPaymentTransactions:"}]}}}